# Language rules

- All **web UI** text (labels, buttons, headings, status badges, tooltips, placeholder text, confirmations) must be in **English**.
- **Podcast content** (episode titles, bullet text, theme/car tag values, transcript text) is in **Danish** and must not be translated.
- Python CLI output (typer.echo, print) that the developer sees in the terminal is English.
- Error messages surfaced to the user in the UI are English.
